    <S id="445">
        <FORM kindOf="original">ihlahlamu hla'alua maci alukala miia ihlaisacu maracanicu tihla'ahlʉ ka pahlumiamiaisa.</FORM>
        <PHON kindOf="original">iɬaɬamu ɬaʔaɾua maʦi aɾukaɾa miia iɬaisaʦu maraʦaniʦu tiɬaʔaɬɨ ka paɬumiamiaisa.</PHON>
        <FORM kindOf="standard">ihlahlamu hla'alua maci alukala miia ihlaisacu maracanicu tihla'ahlʉ ka pahlumiamiaisa.</FORM>
        <PHON kindOf="standard">iɬaɬamu ɬaʔaɾua maʦi aɾukaɾa miia iɬaisaʦu maraʦaniʦu tiɬaʔaɬɨ ka paɬumiamiaisa.</PHON>
